de.frauas.jdemandmodel.reader

Class OwnershipReader

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.frauas.jdemandmodel.reader.CSVReader
      • de.frauas.jdemandmodel.reader.OwnershipReader

  • public class OwnershipReader
extends CSVReader
    This class reads for each appliance a probability of that appliance being installed in a dwelling. The reading will take place during the constructor call. To access the probabilities use the method "get".
    Author:
    lukas
